description: Application for non-material amendments following a grant of planning permission PA/07/02294 dated 10 June 2008 for the following alterations to the tenure and dwelling mix:   Unit mix  From: 1 x 1 bed; 54 x 3 bed; 48 x 4 bed and 3 x 5 bed To: 1 x studio; 55 x 3 bed; 47 x 4 bed and 3 x 5 bed  Tenure allocation  From  21 social rented ( 2 x 3 bed / 16 x 4 bed & 3 x 5 bed) 11 intermediate ( 6 x 3 bed, 5x 4 bed) 74 private ( 1 x 1 bed; 46 x 3 bed & 27 x 4 bed)  To  42 social rented (25 x 3 bed; 17 x 4 bed 63 Intermediate (30 x 3 bed; 30 x 4 bed & 3 x 5 bed) 1x1 private.
